    <abstract>Separate English translations of Sanskrit and Chinese versions of the Larger and
        Smaller Sukhāvatī Sutras are offered in Gómez (1996). Gómez uses the Kumārajīva version of
        the Smaller Sutra, with some reference to Xuanzang’s version.</abstract>
